<div class="field field-type-image">
  
  
                <div class="field-item"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.cancerresearchuk.org/sites/default/files/styles/cruk_no_style/public/research_careers_individual_hd_300dpi_960px.png?itok=wPeZcmRg"   alt="Research Careers" title="Research Careers" /></div>
      
        </div>


<div class="field field-type-text-with-summary">
  
  
                <div class="field-item"><p>We offer a range of fellowships, bursaries and other support to help outstanding scientists and clinicians develop their independent research careers.</p>
<div class="more">
